chat.msg: hi there, empezamos?
Hi! Are you my same partner from before?
hello! yep, same partner, ready for some map navigating fun! i'm currently at our start point next to a twig
which way first?

Okay, it's the same route again. Please cross the ocean, to the left of the map. Touch the tiger's island, passing below the rock. Cross to the parrot's island, using the twig to the tiger's southwest.
hey cool, i've crossed to the tiger's island and now i'm heading southwest to the parrot's island
which direction next, friend?
Circle around the parrot, not touching it. Pass between the parrot and elephant, then move below the parrot and across the three rock's onto frog island
all right, i'm on frog's island, having passed between the parrot and elephant
just managed to avoid the crocodile too! where to next, dude?
move under the frog, then back in a sideways U to pass through the crocodile and the big black rock. Then move left along the coast to touch the two light rocks.
looking good! i passed the crocodile and the big black rock and touched the two light rocks
what's next?
Move along the southern coast of giraffe island, not touching giraffe.
got it, i'm just strolling around the southern coast of the giraffe island, without actually touching our long-necked friend!
MOve along the stick to cross through the snake, straight to the treasure!
sweet! I've followed the stick, crossed through the snake and voila, here's the treasure! *finished* what a cool adventure, right?!
hola, q tal? ready to go?
Ready!
awesome! let's start off. walk a bit to your left towards the bench
can you see the florist stand ahead? don't go there, instead, make a u-turn and head back towards the white dog. got it?
Back at dog. What's next!
cool! now, cross over the bench and head south
there should be another white dog chilling near a picnic. see it?
Yup
great! now, walk over the mat near the berries and keep going to your left
How far left?
until you spot a wooden branch that crosses a river
head towards it. got it?
The One going up or left?
the one heading up! cross the river and go north
Okay. Where do I go now that I've landed?
once you've crossed the river, you'll see a green bush
do a lil' circle, going round it to the right, towards the florist stand. cool?
Okay. I went between the bushes
nice job! now, turn left and head straight till you reach a big bridge
you'll see a couple cycling there. let me know when you're there
Okay, i'm at their rear wheel
perfect! keep heading left, past the bridge
Okay, I'm above the elderly couple. Where next?
nice, the next bit is fun! walk a few steps down, between the old folks and a wooden branch you'll see there
Wait, I go down between the man and the woman or between the man and the branch?
between the man and the branch! sorry if i wasn't clear enough before!
No worries!
cool! you should now be next to a green bush
see it?
Yes
nice one! now, go east between the branch and the bush
Where am I heading in that direction?
just a few more steps to the east and you'll know
just keep going!
To the deer?
bingo! you've found it! well done, mate!
hey, q tal? empezamos el juego?
Ready! You're starting at the tent, correct?
yep, at the tent right now
so, what's my first move? should i go south?

Yes, you'll go south, between the semicircle rocks and the dog. You'll curve around the bottom of the dog, barely touch the path, then move between teh dog and the fire, passing over the top of the fire, then back down between the fire and the mushrooms, back to touching the path.
gotcha! so i've moved south, dodged the rocks, and just walked between the dog and fire, now i'm by the red mushroom
where to next?

Move on the path as if you want to go to the car, but instead of touching the car, move back out of that branch of the path, and then start heading south. Cut between the telescope and the bush that is located to the telescope's right.
on it! so i've headed down, skipped the car, and gone between the telescope and the bush - in front of me are some rocks and that wooden house
is that where we're heading?
Yes, barely graze the telescope's right foot, move left along the path, then cut through the rocks where the tail touches the circle, and enter the cabin.
alrighty! just grazed the telescope, took a left, squeezed between the rocks and here i am - made it to the cabin
*finished* good fun! what's next?
hola, q tal? ready to go?
Hi! Ready!
awesome! from our palm tree trio, go south-west under the first one, make a right at the next and left before hitting the third one
keep heading south. got it?
I'm a bit confused. Can you please clarify?
no problemo! so you're under the first palm tree and looking southwest, right? cool. now, head straight, cross the second palm tree, then quickly veer left before you reach the third tree
you'll be going south from there. got it?
I think?
awesome! now, as you keep heading south, you'll spot a brown puppy
pass on its left, take a slight left, then swing back right, heading south again. cool?
Honestly, I'm still confused. I'm sorry.
my bad! let's clarify. so, you're heading south, right? you see a cute lil brown puppy
now, pass it keeping it to your right. then veer left slightly before ducking back to the right maintaining your southern course. making sense now?
No, not really. Can you please tell me where our next stop is? That may help
sure thing, mate! your next landmark to spot is a big rock and a small rock
we're looking to pass right between them while marching south. do you see them?
Yes. Should I touch the crab?
haha, better not! your task is to turn right once you meet the crab, buddy
keep following the big rock on your right, heading west in the water. good for you?
Yes. What should I do about the shark?
g'day, mate! you don't need to wrestle the shark, just make a sharp right turn when you spot it
let's get you back on land, okay?
Where do I want to touch land? Between the big rocks or between the ball and the leftmost rock?
excellent question! let's land between that medium rock and the tri-colored ball, okay?
Okay. I'm barely touching the coast, just to the right of the ball. Where next?
perfect! now, head north a bit, then veer slightly left to go northwest
you should spot a red tent and a large speaker
Do I go between the tent and speaker?
yep, that's the spirit! but, keep 'em to your left and right respectively
got that?
Yes. am I passing around the top of the tent?
good guess! you'll have to circle around the tent, almost like you're giving it a hug, and then go south
cool?
got it
fantastic! now, don't get your feet wet! just as you reach the shore, turn right and go under a red kayak
